T1  - Stock liquidity and signaling sustainability in emerging markets: Voluntary ESG disclosure, firm valuation, and institutional investor participation
AU  - Lavin, Jaime F.
AU  - Buchuk, Paulo
AU  - Valle, Mauricio A.
AU  - Magner, Nicolás S.
